game.name: Tog Jungle Runner
game.description:
Hey friends, the time has come when you can show your running skills in this awesome adventure game for boys! Try hard and help Tog avoid the massive hurdles in Tog Jungle Runner game. He trusts on your skills and knows very well that you can make him bounce, swing, jump and glide through the dangerous jungle. We know that the task is really difficult to complete. In this free online running game, you also have to take care of collecting as many fruits as you can. This will give you the power to destroy the hurdles and encourage you to get ahead in the game.  

One of the finest html5 games to play, Tog Jungle Runner features dynamic graphics, easy control and outstanding audio and video effects. You will find out a number of obstacles on the way. So, all you need to open your mind to avoid them and reach the destination point. Use the space key to jump in this cool adventure game. Press the space key twice to jump higher. In order to go fast for some time, you can press the right arrow key. The faster you run on the track, the higher points you will be able to collect in this exclusively-designed running game.  

Scoring a big score will make your way to reach on the podium where only the best can reach. All you need to use your patience and running skills in order to win this cute adventure game. Hope you will play with full of confidence and share the final score with your friends. This is an addicting game, so you will definitely come here and play it again and again to fulfill your fantasy for the running games.
